      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKEVIEW LIAM (8) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at four of 19 starts including nine wins but missed the frame latest when eighth (26.35) over 460m at Warragul. Form here is sound including five wins. Drawn wide but with a clean break will be tough to beat again. MINTER SCORCH (1) ran below best last time finishing seventh (29.09) over 510m at this track from Box 6. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Cannot be underestimated. JOROGUMO (4) had the drop on the lead from the rails draw last start but could only manage second, beaten 1.75 lengths (24.60) at this track in a Free For All over 435m. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Must be included in calculations. MATILDA ROSE (2) has top-three aspirations after placing at big odds last time.",
